data.name: GoGoConf 2019
data.description: GoGoConf is an international Go (Golang) developers conference that takes place in Krakow, Poland on October 25th. Have an opportunity to meet other Go developers, have a chat with speakers from companies like solarisBank, Allegro, Filestack, BBVA and many others.
